{"tid":1319731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察隊員佐級協會林志偉批評有示威者行為如「野獸」","createTime":"2019-07-15T08:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:36:21.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87f5ecc17fc5c53d31cd613d13f2e29b195cf720","tid":1319731,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉回應昨晚沙田警民衝突時說，警方現時所面對的已並非一般示威者，而是有組織、有充分資源、有完善計劃的對手。對於昨日的情況，警員被示威者暴力圍毆、有警員被咬斷手指，亦有警員手指骨被扭至變形，反問警員與示威者有何深仇大恨，批評有關行為如「野獸」一樣。<br />\n<br />\n被問到警隊是否成為「磨心」，林志偉說，警隊在過往不同大事都必然走上最前線，他們並無反感，因為警隊職責就是要執法、維護香港法治，但今次事件，似乎港人已摒棄法治，如果市民漠視警隊維護法治的努力，將對警隊是很大傷害。<br />\n<br />\n對於有立法會議員質疑警方昨日行動的部署不當，林志偉說，警隊的部署及戰術沒有必然性，他不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林志偉說，他會因應昨晚的情況，向管理層反映意見，如將來面對可預見的情況，能作更適當的行動調配，例如保護裝備、使用武力的層次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468435-20190715.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468435-20190715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=0fbeafb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468435-20190715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a08820de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468435-20190715.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"cfb695c50eca4798da67b95e6f3dc1c3fbdca249","tid":1319731,"uid":177089,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKjxHSO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKjxHSO.png&h=cc6d83ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n示威者係野獸 警察係咪殺手？"},{"pid":"102e6ea05c1928882efa0ced0e96000678d05186","tid":1319731,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cfb695c50eca4798da67b95e6f3dc1c3fbdca249","tid":1319731,"uid":177089,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKjxHSO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKjxHSO.png&h=cc6d83ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n示威者係野獸 警察係咪殺手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a10dbb383a754a601f710e848312eb9ffb594f","tid":1319731,"uid":2772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"啱喎<br />\n困獸鬥又係你攪既<br />\n咁你D警犬成隻禽獸咁<br />\n人地做返野獸行為抵抗都唔俾?<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會同鬣狗講道理?"},{"pid":"1ba1537706367bc3ae90e072fdb0797ec9cb4631","tid":1319731,"uid":113544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"林渣同佢班mk又伸個龜頭出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除咗批評譴責之外，你仲識啲咩字眼呀閪仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb80a60e0f2284192ca65fb9db606e721fb559e","tid":1319731,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉回應昨晚沙田警民衝突時說，警方現時所面對的已並非一般示威者，而是有組織、有充分資源、有完善計劃的對手。對於昨日的情況，警員被示威者暴力圍毆、有警員被咬斷手指，亦有警員手指骨被扭至變形，<span style=\"color: red;\">反問警員與示威者有何深仇大恨</span>，批評有關行為如「野獸」一樣。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n有咩深仇大恨？<br />\n自己睇睇69 612班狗做過啲咩啦<br />\n我地仲有6個以死相諫！<br />\n呢啲仇唔係班狗比人暴力圍毆、咬斷手指、手指骨被扭至變形就發洩到架"},{"pid":"0cd74c8ef0b752f1aa7b75a3830d78e903fd0b46","tid":1319731,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"野獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3A1BkZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3A1BkZ.png&h=a66ef224&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e68040fbcc45ea9aa250b19d7a4935549d3bfda3","tid":1319731,"uid":6385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c